.sp
\fBclush\fP \fB\-a\fP | \fB\-g\fP \fIgroup\fP | \fB\-w\fP \fInodes\fP  [OPTIONS] \-\-copy
\fIfile\fP | \fIdir\fP [ \fIfile\fP | \fIdir\fP ...] [ \-\-dest \fIdest_path\fP ]
